title: GraphicRiver - Pixelator Photoshop Action
description:
Pixelator Photoshop Action

Create professional 3D pixel art from your photos with a few clicks! Below are a few action features:
Choose from 4 extrusion angles.
Choose from 5 extrusion depths.
Choose any pixel size.
Pixel groups are broken down into folders â€“ so you can be creative by duplicating/hiding folders to create additional effects.
Easy to export your design on a transparent background.
Each pixel set has its own shadow created.
When brushing over your photo, even using a soft brush will create a perfect pixel edge
